{"tid":81960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不堪朋友嘲笑　英國男童彎刀自行割包皮","createTime":"2017-01-15T15:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T16:17:50.000Z","uid":6555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31e3bfc6d6de7eda88f12398d0df9738252a16b3","tid":81960,"uid":6555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"不堪朋友嘲笑　英國男童彎刀自行割包皮<br />\n<br />\n不少專家都指出，孩童成長期間，朋輩的影響不容忽視。英國早前就有一名男童，懷疑因不堪朋友的嘲笑，而在家中以一把大彎刀為自己進行割包皮手術，導致下體大量出血，並自行到醫院求助。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，受傷男童因為受到朋友的恫嚇，指他假若不進行割包皮手術，就永遠得不到女孩子的垂青。男童擔憂朋友的說話會成真，於是以彎刀割掉自己的包皮，導致下體大量出血。男童立即到醫院求醫，並花了兩天接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n醫院內的一名醫生表示，不明白男孩的動機，因為當地社區有免費的上門割包皮手術；另有醫護人員為男孩的「勇敢」而感到震驚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400b7a7bbbc0548ed3f24047f39b410fdb65dade","tid":81960,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505ed0a5c552b324234fead851f6f9cd7e9c1a1a","tid":81960,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986f157df36c78a65442a679d3f99fd48fe9ed54","tid":81960,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfdf18ade40943fbd1b3393403b8dc734454a30","tid":81960,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fb76679dfc0ce4cddc1931d7c727c86d23f19c","tid":81960,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"話唔埋找j數"},{"pid":"e10f7c1ded3869252341b4578da68228a11d324b","tid":81960,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"有呢種刀好大機會係蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}